Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I can sense that\Nyour wish and my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,...are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,...why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Tea and pickled plums\Nwork best for hangovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:12.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What a sad drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}, look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going out with her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sour...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Have fun, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,All right. Let your kind,\Nbig brother here send you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,She refused me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,If a pillar goes there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:09.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:14.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:18.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:04:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of couples...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think we really fit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.68,Main,,0,0,0,,There could be a wonderful encounter, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone might pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Pick up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,--Y-Yuzuki, were you asked out before?!\N--Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?! How was he?\NHow did he ask you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Oh, come on, let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,So, did you go out someplace with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really not worth talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww... No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me! I want to know! I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,"Girl meets Girl Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,"Lunch bag" "Warmer cover"\N"Handkerchief" "Accessory pouch" "Welcome"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I can afford this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Coaster"\NYup. This is more like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get this for Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to see Ruko having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:54.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy you a\Nmatching pair of scrunchies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Look. Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right! Can I get a closer look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It's quiet over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take a short break?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. My friends in Aomori\Nasked me to take a pic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I wrote to them that I made friends in Tokyo,\Nand they sent me an e-mail asking for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Show me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I kept...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...wishing for friends, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...I guess I had friends all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should get a mobile, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,If I have a mobile, then I can\Nget in touch with friends quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It helps if something happens,\Nor if I'm far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,--Say, can I take a look?\N--Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we go\Nshopping for mobiles next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But are you sure you'll\Nbe able to use one, Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it that hard to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm... I guess we'll go to Akihabara then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--No matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I go far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You can only buy mobiles in Akihabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Not true! They were being\Nsold near my place too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, only the mobile itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't sign-up except in Akihabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She's lying. You can buy them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? You surprised me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You better discuss it with your grandma, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm getting thirsty. How about\Nwe get something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,...why ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on! There's no one around! You know why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have caramel flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe? Let's get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.92,Main,,0,0,0,,"Group A"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What gives, having a competition\Nat a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Are there any... Selectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,There's... one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,A Selector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,She's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Closer... She's coming closer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you battle me, please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,She's... a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry there for my girl's loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,See, look Eldora!\NIt's exactly like Chiyori said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you we could find Selectors here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,And two of them! Could this be fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Duh, they're having a competition.\NOf course you'd find some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess us heroines can't\Navoid the fate of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Avoid? You're looking for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Pooh! Eldora, go with the flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! She's like this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So, anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Please battle Chiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The back alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm...! So battle-ly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, did you folks go\Nto Urazoe Iona's fan event?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You went, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, we just couldn't make it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Eldora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...? What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,My kid here is lousy with directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It took a couple hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,circling around the area over and over again,\Njust to find the location earlier. The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora... zip your mouth! Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,G-G-Give! I give! I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,So, anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The beautiful maidens' battle for\Ntheir wishes is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We... won't battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not going to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you're Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish won't come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't know what\Nhappens if you lose your battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What...! Are...! You saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I knowey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Death awaits those who lose seven times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,The WIXOSS factors\Nspread inside your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...then from the inside you\Ngo {\i1}kaboom{\i0}! {\i1}Squish{\i0}! {\i1}Splat{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose three times, you lose\Nyour rights and wish, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...that very wish is reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish was to be wealthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Losing in battle means that you lose all wealth,\Nand plummeted to poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish was to become\Nskilled in playing the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You may lose your piano, or you may\Nbecome incapable of playing the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, you won't be able\Nto play the piano, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:38.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's wish was "to make friends"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,With that wish reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish reversed? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...a new setting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish came true\Nwithout relying on WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But, but, getting your happiness\Nthrough battling is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,--Winning in battle...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Winning in battle isn't\Ngoing to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Winning battles aren't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't become an Eternal Girl\Nwithout your LRIG accepting your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I... accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,And...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yessy, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"How an LRIG is Born"! The second\Nvolume to the WIXOSS novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS 2! {\i1}The Flames of Void{\i0}\N{\i1}Play the Victory Song of Oblivion{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's how you get\Nyour wish to come truey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... Show me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,--Say, Chiyori?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you... remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I sensed something I felt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori, Chiyori! It's her, you know? Her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the one who beat you in\Nyour very first battle you offered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Whaaaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Why are you a card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish came true, and I replaced my LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Look carefully... This is what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't go to school or\Neat ice cream any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Even the person I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama can't make Ruko into an LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to say bye to Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you win the battles,\Nyou're going to become just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're an LRIG, then you must know about\Nthat white windowed room, and that girl, Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you letting her battle\Nknowing what happens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, my memories have\Nbeen fleeting recently and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,...I have no idea\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems she understands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:15.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you shouldn't battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaaaaaah{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It's exactly the same as the novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The heroine becomes a card,\Nand the story is to be continued!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:28.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Going into the world of WIXOSS\Nis like, Chiyori's dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,--So happy!\N--Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiyo-rinda{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyo-ringa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyo-rumba, Chori-Chori...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Which do you think is better for\Nmy name when I become an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think you need one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Eldora, I bet you think Chiyori\Ncan't get her wish to come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,No-I-believe-in-you-from-the-bottom-of-my-heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Why the monotone read?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Ru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:23.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait...! Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru... Tama will battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This will be the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,White Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko won, so why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.77,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't... Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, a new Eternal Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with the long face, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.76,Main,,0,0,0,,My Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to\Nwhat Urith was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san {\i0}won more than enough battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you lacked a condition\Nto get your wish to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,So the condition was met,\Nand your wish came true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}, what is your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,To be an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,To become an LRIG to someone stronger\Nthan me, so as to continue battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So the last condition was to lose in battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish came true\Nbecause you lost to Ruko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,But, how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad... Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did Tama go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You should have... battled her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to meet Tama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That wish may come true... If you battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,No. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why do you still have me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to battle,\Nyou should throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it. You want to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Such attachment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring her with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you wanted to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,If you battled again, there's\Nno telling what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She's right! Tama disappearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona becoming Ruko's card...\NNo one could have expected it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Something worse may happen next!\N--But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I want to meet Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I still... I want to help Yuzuki,\Nand everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:13.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I know... I know, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do either,\Nso let's all think together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. You're not alone, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,We're with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's all get through this, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,There are too many things I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Why isn't Ruko battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Like me, she seeks battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,And her wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to help Yuzuki, and everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,An LRIG only accepts a wish\Nthey believe they can make true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite abandoning the wish,\Nwhy did she believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...she could make such an\Nimpossible wish come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko's LRIG... is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll change Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead of clinging on to an impossible wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,...I want her to sense the excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,To battle to her heart's desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Along with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Next is Shinjuku. Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my clue... to find Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:21:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Silent Beginning"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Silent Beginning"\NNothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the "now" handed to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I begin to walk in the morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a world where light and dark intersect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}catharsis begins to awake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:48.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swore in my shaking heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I won't lose anyone anymore...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my tears flow tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll run through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release myself towards the future I selected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to regain it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:27.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up on my wish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It was Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be spouting that crap's name\Nwith that crap voice of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut it, twerp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:43.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If there's a battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mastermind...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Feverish Bond"\NThat Feverish Bond.
